longBusinessSummary: Sustainable Development Acquisition I Corp. does not have significant operations. The company focuses on effecting a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization or similar business combination with one or more businesses or entities. It intends to effectuate initial business combination using cash from the proceeds of initial public offerings and the sale of the private placement shares, company shares, debt or a combination of cash, equity, and debt. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Bakersfield, California.
